column6:
Beautiful house located in Rancho Viejo Golf & Country Club with a private pool, outdoor terrace and access to the golf course. It's a perfect place for couples, families (with kids) and big groups.

If you like golf, want to go shopping or just a relaxing vacation the place to go!

Sleeps up to 12 on a master bedroom (King bed), full bath w/tub; 2nd bedroom (1 double, 1 singe beds) full bath; 3rd bedroom (6 single beds) full bath adjacent.

Incredible location!
Free Wifi!
column9: Awesome House with Pool in Rancho Viejo Golf Club
